  <title translate="true">Clickers (eInstruction IR, RF, Renaissance)</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Clickers (eInstruction IR, RF, Renaissance)</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Header 2" style="text-align:right;"><link displaytype="image" src="New_Back_Arrow_icon.gif" type="topiclink" href="Assessment"></link><text styleclass="Header 2" style="font-size:8pt;" translate="true">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Assessment" styleclass="Answer" style="font-size:8pt;" translate="true">Return to Assessment Menu</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab /><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[What Student Response Systems are supported by the Elements™  Clicker Software?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Currently supported clickers are listed below:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">eInstruction® - RF, IR and Pulse</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Renaissance Clickers</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">We are currently researching and developing support for additional clickers. &#160;This list will be updated as more clickers are supported.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab /><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[How do I obtain the Elements™ Clicker Software? ]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">In order to obtain the Elements clicker software please contact your district administrator or Thinkgate Support (if permitted) to receive the software.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab /><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[Do I need to install anything else besides the Elements™ Clicker Software?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">If you are using the eInstruction® IR, eInstruction® RF, or Renaissance clickers you will not need to install any additional software. &#160;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">However, if you are using the eInstruction® Pulse clickers you will need to install the CPS software that is located on the eInstruction software.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;"><image src="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Normal"></image><tab /><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_plus0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_plus1.gif" styleclass="Normal"><caption translate="true"><![CDATA[How do I administer a assessment using the Elements™  Clicker Software?]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:42px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Answer"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">In order to administer an assessment utilizing the Elements clicker software, please follow the steps below:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Answer"></para>
          <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px; font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; color:#000080;">
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Verify proper software is installed (</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Elements</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Clicker</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Software</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">CPS</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Software</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> if using </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Pulse</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> clickers)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Verify </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Receiver</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> is properly plugged in</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Open the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Elements</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Clicker</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Software</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Enter in your </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">user</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">ID</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">password</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true">(same one used to access Elements)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Log</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">In</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Enter the </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Test</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">ID</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> into the Test ID field</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;" translate="true"> (the test ID is located on the dashboard for the test event)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Load</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Test</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Enter the appropriate </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Pad</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">#&apos;s</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> in the Pad # column for each student (click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Enter</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> after typing in the number)</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Once a student&apos;s clicker information is entered their clicker will auto receive the test</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Once the clicker is ready the student can proceed through the test</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Answer" style="margin-left:48px;"><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true">Click </text><text styleclass="Answer" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Finished</text><text styleclass="Answer" translate="true"> once all results are entered to submit scores</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
